ActCanada National Parks Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 5 to the Canada National Parks Act (Sunshine Village Ski Area)
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE 5 to the Canada National Parks Act (Sunshine Village Ski Area) in order to add the name and description of the commercial ski area in the vicinity of Sunshine Village in Banff National Park of Canada, as was intended when the Canada National Parks Act was created in 2000.
